#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

cat <<'EOF'
Project Dev Tools
=================

Install:
  just install                         Install Elixir and Node dependencies
  just install npm:<pkg> <version> --app <app>
                                       Add <pkg>@<version> to a Node app
  just install hex:<pkg> <version> --app <app>
                                       Add <pkg>@<version> to an Elixir app

Remove:
  just remove                          Remove Elixir and Node dependencies
  just remove npm                      Remove node_modules only
  just remove hex                      Remove Elixir deps only
  just remove npm:<pkg> --app <app>
                                       Remove <pkg> from a Node app
  just remove hex:<pkg> --app <app>
                                       Remove <pkg> from an Elixir app

Update:
  just update recipes                  Refresh the managed just recipes

Check:
  just check specs [PATH...]           Check TLA+, Alloy, and OpenAPI specs
  just check types [PATH...]           Typecheck TypeScript apps under paths
  just check knip                      Check unused files, dependencies, and exports

Test:
  just test [PATH...]                  Run tests for selected apps

Build:
  just build [PATH...]                 Build or compile selected apps

Database:
  just migrate db                      Run Phoenix database migrations
  just reset db                        Drop, recreate, migrate, and seed the database

Dev:
  just dev [PROCESS...]                Run devservers with process-compose
  just dev --dry-run                   Validate process-compose.yaml without starting servers

Lint:
  just lint [PATH...]                  Lint configured Elixir, JS, TS, and CSS paths

Format:
  just format [PATH...]                Format configured JS, CSS, and Elixir paths
  just format --check [PATH...]        Check configured JS, CSS, and Elixir paths
EOF
